==English==

===Etymology===
''[[re-]]'' + ''[[cycle]]''.

===Verb===
{{wikipedia|Recycling}}
{{en-verb|recycl|es}}

# {{transitive}} To [[break down]] and [[reuse]] component materials.
#: '''''Recycled''' paper.''
#: '''''Recycled''' plastic.''
# {{transitive}} To [[reuse]] as a whole.
# {{intransitive|ergative}} To be recycled.
#: ''Sulfur '''recycles''' in the sulfur cycle.''

